    "## Step 5 — Visualisation\n",
    "The visualisation section is where the intern demonstrates they understand what they computed,\n",
    "not just how to run the code. A heatmap of the similarity matrix, combined with a bar chart of topsimilar players for a chosen target, makes the mathematical structure visible.\n"
   ]
